---

<LayoutPages title="Personalizados - deja que vuele tu creatividad">
  <article
    class="w-full min-h-24 mx-auto rounded-md p-2 relative flex items-center justify-center shadow-md mb-20 md:mb-28"
  >
    <div
      class="absolute p-2 md:p-4 bg-white w-[70%] md:max-w-[65%] z-20 mx-auto md:w-full min-h-28 flex items-center justify-center gap-y-0 flex-col border-dashed border-2 -mb-8"
    >
      <h1 class="text-base md:text-xl text-primary-txt font-bold text-center">
        Pastelería Personalizada
      </h1>
      <h2 class="text-lg md:text-4xl text-[#f1683a] font-bold text-center">
        Crea momentos únicos
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xs md:text-base text-center text-balance font-semibold">
        <strong class="text-primary-txt">¡Tu idea ! ,</strong>
        Nuestro diseño
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
  <article>
    <h3 class="text-base md:text-2xl text-balance font-bold pl-4 md:pl-0">
      Recomendados
    </h3>
    <hr />
    <p class="text-xs md:text-base text-balance pl-4 md:pl-0 my-4">
      Te presentamos algunas opciones que hemos seleccionado especialmente para
      inspirarte. Si no encuentras exactamente lo que buscas, más abajo
      encontrarás un formulario donde podrás compartir tus ideas y personalizar
      tu pedido a tu gusto. ¡Queremos dar vida a tus ideas!
    </p>
  </article>
  <article>
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-y-14 p-5 w-full mb-10 md:mb-16"
    >
      {
        personalizados.map((per) => (
          <CardProducts
            id={per.id}
            descuento={per.descuento}
            image={per.imagen}
            nombre={per.nombre}
            precio={per.precio}
          />
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </article>
  <article>
    <h4 class="text-lg md:text-xl text-balance font-bold mb-2">
      <strong class="text-primary-txt">¿Tienes una idea en mente? </strong>
      ¡Nosotros la hacemos dulce realidad!
    </h4>
    <p class="text-xs md:text-base text-balance pl-4 md:pl-0 my-3">
      Cuéntanos qué tienes en mente. Completa el formulario a continuación y
      recibirás una respuesta de nuestra parte lo antes posible. ¡Estamos
      emocionados de hacer tus ideas realidad!
    </p>
    <hr />

    <div class="w-full p-4 my-10">
      <form class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="relative z-0 w-full mb-5 group">
          <input
            type="email"
            name="floating_email"
            id="floating_email"
            class="block py-2.5 px-0 w-full text-sm text-gray-900 bg-transparent border-0 border-b-2 border-gray-300 appearance-none dark:text-white dark:border-gray-600 dark:focus:border-blue-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 focus:border-blue-600 peer"
            placeholder=" "
            required
          />
          <label
            for="floating_email"
            class="peer-focus:font-medium absolute text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 duration-300 transform -translate-y-6 scale-75 top-3 -z-10 origin-[0] peer-focus:start-0 rtl:peer-focus:translate-x-1/4 rtl:peer-focus:left-auto peer-focus:text-blue-600 peer-focus:dark:text-blue-500 peer-placeholder-shown:scale-100 peer-placeholder-shown:translate-y-0 peer-focus:scale-75 peer-focus:-translate-y-6"
            >Correo electronico</label
          >
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-6">
          <div class="relative z-0 w-full mb-5 group">
            <input
              type="text"
              name="floating_first_name"
              id="floating_first_name"
              class="block py-2.5 px-0 w-full text-sm text-gray-900 bg-transparent border-0 border-b-2 border-gray-300 appearance-none dark:text-white dark:border-gray-600 dark:focus:border-blue-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 focus:border-blue-600 peer"
              placeholder=" "
              required
            />
            <label
              for="floating_first_name"
              class="peer-focus:font-medium absolute text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 duration-300 transform -translate-y-6 scale-75 top-3 -z-10 origin-[0] peer-focus:start-0 rtl:peer-focus:translate-x-1/4 peer-focus:text-blue-600 peer-focus:dark:text-blue-500 peer-placeholder-shown:scale-100 peer-placeholder-shown:translate-y-0 peer-focus:scale-75 peer-focus:-translate-y-6"
              >Nombres</label
            >
          </div>
          <div class="relative z-0 w-full mb-5 group">
            <input
              type="text"
              name="floating_last_name"
              id="floating_last_name"
              class="block py-2.5 px-0 w-full text-sm text-gray-900 bg-transparent border-0 border-b-2 border-gray-300 appearance-none dark:text-white dark:border-gray-600 dark:focus:border-blue-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 focus:border-blue-600 peer"
              placeholder=" "
              required
            />
            <label
              for="floating_last_name"
              class="peer-focus:font-medium absolute text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 duration-300 transform -translate-y-6 scale-75 top-3 -z-10 origin-[0] peer-focus:start-0 rtl:peer-focus:translate-x-1/4 peer-focus:text-blue-600 peer-focus:dark:text-blue-500 peer-placeholder-shown:scale-100 peer-placeholder-shown:translate-y-0 peer-focus:scale-75 peer-focus:-translate-y-6"
              >Apellidos</label
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-6">
          <div class="relative z-0 w-full mb-5 group">
            <input
              type="tel"
              pattern="[0-9]{3}-[0-9]{3}-[0-9]{4}"
              name="floating_phone"
              id="floating_phone"
              class="block py-2.5 px-0 w-full text-sm text-gray-900 bg-transparent border-0 border-b-2 border-gray-300 appearance-none dark:text-white dark:border-gray-600 dark:focus:border-blue-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 focus:border-blue-600 peer"
              placeholder=" "
              required
            />
            <label
              for="floating_phone"
              class="peer-focus:font-medium absolute text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 duration-300 transform -translate-y-6 scale-75 top-3 -z-10 origin-[0] peer-focus:start-0 rtl:peer-focus:translate-x-1/4 peer-focus:text-blue-600 peer-focus:dark:text-blue-500 peer-placeholder-shown:scale-100 peer-placeholder-shown:translate-y-0 peer-focus:scale-75 peer-focus:-translate-y-6"
              >Numero de telefono (123-456-7890)</label
            >
          </div>
          <div class="relative z-0 w-full mb-5 group">
            <input
              type="text"
              name="floating_company"
              id="floating_company"
              class="block py-2.5 px-0 w-full text-sm text-gray-900 bg-transparent border-0 border-b-2 border-gray-300 appearance-none dark:text-white dark:border-gray-600 dark:focus:border-blue-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 focus:border-blue-600 peer"
              placeholder=" "
              required
            />
            <label
              for="floating_company"
              class="peer-focus:font-medium absolute text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 duration-300 transform -translate-y-6 scale-75 top-3 -z-10 origin-[0] peer-focus:start-0 rtl:peer-focus:translate-x-1/4 peer-focus:text-blue-600 peer-focus:dark:text-blue-500 peer-placeholder-shown:scale-100 peer-placeholder-shown:translate-y-0 peer-focus:scale-75 peer-focus:-translate-y-6"
              >Direccion (opcionar)</label
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative z-0 w-full mb-5 group">
          <label
            for="message"
            class="block mb-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
            >Tu mensaje</label
          >
          <textarea
            id="message"
            rows="4"
            class="block p-2.5 w-full text-sm text-gray-900 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:border-gray-600 dark:placeholder-gray-400 dark:text-white dark:focus:ring-blue-500 dark:focus:border-blue-500"
            placeholder="Cuentanos tu idea..."></textarea>
        </div>
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="text-white w-full bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-800 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm sm:w-auto px-5 py-2.5 text-center dark:bg-blue-600 dark:hover:bg-blue-700 dark:focus:ring-blue-800"
          >Submit</button
        >
      </form>
    </div>
  </article>
</LayoutPages>
